### GMOB API - Exemplos de Requisições

### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### 1. Registrar novo corretor
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome_completo": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "telefone": "(11) 99999-9999",
  "cpf": "123.456.789-00",
  "senha": "senha123",
  "perfil": "administrador"
}

### 2. Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "senha": "senha123"
}

### 3. Obter perfil do usuário logado
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Criar novo corretor (apenas admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/corretor
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome_completo": "Maria Santos",
  "email": "maria@email.com",
  "telefone": "(11) 88888-8888",
  "cpf": "987.654.321-00",
  "senha": "senha456",
  "perfil": "corretor"
}

### 5. Listar todos os corretores (apenas admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/corretor?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Buscar corretor por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/corretor/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Atualizar corretor
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/corretor/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome_completo": "João Silva Atualizado",
  "telefone": "(11) 77777-7777"
}

### 8. Remover corretor (apenas admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/corretor/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Teste de rate limiting (executar múltiplas vezes)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "senha": "senha_errada"
}

###

